Faaduma Sahra Muxamed waa [[xaas]]kii [[asxaabi]] iyo [[khaliif|Khaliif Ar-Raashid]] [[Cali|Cali binu Abi Daalib]], hooyada [[mataan]]aha [[Xasan]] iyo [[Xuseen]] iyo qofta shanaad ee '''Ahlu-Beytka,''' Sababtoo ah waxay aad ugu dhowayd, daryeeli jirtey isla markaana taageeri jirtey aabaheed Nebi Muxamed, Faadumo Sahra waa mid ka mid ah dumarka loogu qadarinta badan yahay [[muslim]]iinta dhexdooda. 

Faaduma nebi waxay dhimatey 13kii Jamadi-al-Awwal [[sanad|sanadkii 11aad]] ee Hijrada (taasi oo u dhiganta [[Arbaco]] Ogosto 5teedii [[wakhti|sanadkii 632]] [[C.D]]) waxaana lagu aasay magaalada [[Medina]], [[Xijaas]] deegaanada [[Carabi]]ya.

= Taariikh nooleedkeeda =

Faaduma waxaa dhalay Nabiga ilaahay [[Nebi Maxamed c.s|muxamad bin cabdilaah]] SC, Hooyadeed waa [[Khaddiija bint Khuwaylid|Khaddiija binti khuweylid]] oo ahayd xaaskii koowaad ee Rasuulka scw, waxey ahayd faaduma ilmaha Rasuulka scw ee Khadiija u dhashay midii ugu yareed, sanadka ay dhalatay khilaaf ayaa ka jira waxey ku tageen culumada [[Sunni|Al-sunaha]] inay dhalatay shan sano ka hor soo saarista Nabiga, Halka [[Shiica|shiicada]] ay qabaan inay dhalatay shan sano ka dib soosaarista Nabiga SC. 

Faaduma waxey kusoo kortay [[makka]], yaraanteeda waxey goob joog u ahayd dhibka ay lagu haayay aabaheed iyo inta yar ay raacsaneyd, waxey ahayd inee saacideyso Nabiga scw, mar waxaa dhacday gaalada inay Nabiga scw oo ujuudsan ay dusha ks saareen mandheerta geela, Nabiga scw kama dhaqaaqin sujuudka faaduma ayaa loo sheegay way soo oroday mandheerta ayee ka tuurtay Nabiga scw<ref>https://www.dorar.net/hadith/sharh/11975</ref>, mudo ka dib waxaa lagu go'doomiyay Nabiga iyo sxaabadiis iyo tolkiisa ree [[Banuu Haashim|banii haashim]] [[shicbi abii daalib]], Nolol adag ayee wajaheen, intii xaaladaas adag lagu jiray ayee faaduma waasay Hooyadeed [[Khadiijo|Khadiija]]. Waxey dareentay murugo iyo xanuun laakin mayna is dhigan waxey ogeed masuuliyada ka saaran aabahey qaasatan markuu waayay xaaskiisa iyo adeerkiis [[abuu daalib]] oo hiil u ahaa, dulqaad ayee muujisay waxey si fiican u dar yeeli jirtay aabaheed [[Nebi Maxamed c.s|nabi muxamad]] heer loogu kunyoodo "'''umu abiihaa'''" yacni aabaheed hooyadiis.    

=Guurkeeda=
Bishii [[Safar (bil)|safar]] sanadkii labaad ee hijiriga Waxaa guursaday [[Cali bin Abii Daalib|Cali bin abii daalib]], oo ina adeer la'ahaa nabiga scw, waxa uuna mahar uga dhigay rati uu gaday 480 dirham ka bixiyay<ref name="المنتظم2">[http://www.al-eman.com/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%AA%D8%A8/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%B8%D9%85+%D9%81%D9%8A+%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%AE+%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%84%D9%88%D9%83+%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%85%D9%85+**/i50&p1 المنتظم في التاريخ] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090113041332/http://www.al-eman.com/IslamLib/viewchp.asp?BID=179&CID=32|date=13 يناير 2009}}</ref>, Cali ka hor waxaa soo doontay saxaabo badan laakin dhamaan Nabiga scw wuu celiayay, waxa uu dhahay ilaahay baa I faray inaa cali ku daro<ref name="شبكة الدرر الدعوية 1">قال[[نبي|النبي]] [[محمد]]: «إن الله تعالى أمرني أن أزوج فاطمه من علي» رواه [[الطبراني]] ورجاله ثقات.</ref>.

Faaduma waxey [[Cali]] u dhashay [[xasan]] iyo [[Xuseen Bin Cali Bin Abii Daalib|xuseen]] si xariir ah sanadihii 3aad iyo afaraad ee Hijrada<ref name="الكامل1">[http://www.al-eman.com/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%AA%D8%A8/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84+%D9%81%D9%8A+%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%AE+**/i46&p1 الكامل في التاريخ- مكتبة نداء الإيمان] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090112123559/http://islamtoday.al-eman.com/Islamlib/viewchp.asp?BID=174&CID=21|date=12 يناير 2009}}</ref>, sidoo kale waxee dhashay [[Zeynaba binti cali|Zeynaba]], [[Umu kaltuum binti cali|umu kaltuum]] iyo muxusin, midkaan dambe khilaaf ayaa ka jiro inuu jiro.

